{
  "stem": "9963.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It is something so inhumane, so uncalled for it-- to take people what didn't do nothing wrong in their life and to do this to them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Then I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't know why something like this should have happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "After that, when I got the letters, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] if I wouldn't have my friends, as I mentioned before, what they were ready to give their lives for me, I would do something to myself because that was something that I could not condone.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I could not go over it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But they helped me a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They sat with me, day and night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They didn't let me alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they talked to me for several days, but I couldn't get over it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Because I was very much heart broken.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said to them, I don't want to live anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If that's happened-- and I know what's happening to the rest of the family that took them to Belzec or to Treblinka to the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I did not want to live anymore, but only with my friends, they talked to me and they said if-- to remember, if I do something to myself, what would happen to them?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they all looked up to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was the-- [SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what-- how to say this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The way I did things for everybody, what everybody is-- was with me, for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I never evaluated my life more than anybody else's.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or matter of fact, I value my life much less because I did things for other people, and that's what made me happy that I could help other people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never took for myself nothing, but only to do something for everybody else.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
